item.title: Internet protocol design
item.description: Project Requirements In automated vehicular systems, if one vehicle needs to overtake the other, a video stream from other vehicles approching it in the same lane needs to be processed and the decision of overtaking or changing the lane has to be made on the basis of other vehicles on the vicinity.
